{
  "stem": "27748.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think it was the mother of this person who said we were the smallest in class.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this woman bragged about how nice she had been to my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She'd give my mother food in exchange for her silver.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I smiled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I smiled all day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was only the next day after I'd left it hit me what this woman had said, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that she had robbed my mother.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She raped my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But the-- on a healthier note, there was one woman, everybody said you have to see Ernestine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You have to talk to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It turned out that Ernestine took care of me as a baby, as far as I know, that she diapered me, she later told me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was a woman who was probably in her 80s when we went there, perhaps 78 or 80.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Everybody had said that she stood by the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And apparently she did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That is, after I left, all the Jews had to give up their houses and they all had to move into one house together, those who still remained.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the whole village distanced themselves from the Jews, except this woman who brought-- who really brought them food, Ernestine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so apparently she was connected to our household somehow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so when I went to see her, she was a very simple, very uneducated, simple woman, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] except she has a heart.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[CRYING] And she showed me pictures and gave me pictures.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I still have them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so she made the difference in that visit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She has since died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I believe she had a daughter who married an American soldier, who moved-- who went to live in Atlanta.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I never found out the name.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
